      <title>莫迪维持借贷政策基本不变，印度债券价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/modi-government-leaves-borrowing-largely-unchanged-bonds-lower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政府令交易员对大幅削减债务的预期感到失望，印度债券市场出现下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/modi-government-leaves-borrowing-largely-unchanged-bonds-lower</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 07:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市创 1 月以来最大跌幅，回到全会前水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/chinese-stocks-see-worst-selloff-since-january-as-mood-sours</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于三中全会后缺乏重大政策支持，加剧了看跌情绪，中国股市遭遇六个月来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/chinese-stocks-see-worst-selloff-since-january-as-mood-sours</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 07:06:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士宝盛任命高盛资深人士布林格为新任首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/julius-baer-picks-goldman-sachs-veteran-bollinger-as-new-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士宝盛集团有限公司 (Julius Baer Group Ltd) 已聘请斯蒂芬·博林格 (Stefan Bollinger) 担任其下一任首席执行官，对于这家瑞士财富管理公司而言，这是一个相对不为人知的选择，该公司正试图摆脱去年的 Signa 房地产丑闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/julius-baer-picks-goldman-sachs-veteran-bollinger-as-new-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 05:17:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡核心通胀率自 2022 年以来首次放缓至 2.9%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/singapore-core-inflation-slows-below-3-first-time-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡六月份核心通胀率的降幅超过预期，使得央行有空间集中精力保护这个贸易依赖型经济免受全球冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/singapore-core-inflation-slows-below-3-first-time-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 05:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾房地产股因在线赌场禁令而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/philippine-property-stocks-tumble-in-online-casino-ban-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯下令禁止针对中国赌客的在线赌场，此举导致周二菲律宾房地产股暴跌，因为赌场关闭可能导致许多办公空间空置。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/philippine-property-stocks-tumble-in-online-casino-ban-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 03:44:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
